You will need to copy 'Flag C', make a new object, paste it twice for ID's 1829 and 1830. (or manually add it yourself.)
The graphics ID's are 12633 and 12634.
25 Frames.
1 Frame Per Angle. Sequence Type 2.

This will create these custom objects to show the x/y values in game. Depending on the map size, it may take really long to generate the scenario...
